transcripts.text: Pastor Dana, I know our time is running so fast.  It's running out.  But you have to share with us the latest dreams that God has given you.  What else has God revealed to you in these dreams that you've been receiving?  And what do we do as the church?  How do we respond to what you saw?  And how do we prepare?

I had a dream this past Friday night, and I shared it Sunday morning live at my church.  I didn't want to do a Facebook one again.  But I had a dream that followed the same pattern of the months, and I saw the calendar turn to September.  And a hand reached up and grabbed the month of September and pulled it off of the page.  And then it laid it down in front of an altar.  And we have a secret place in our church that we built about seven, eight years ago.  Our altar has horns on it, just like the one mentioned in the Bible.  We have the four carnal doctrines of the Son of God are on pictures in there.  And I saw the month of September laid down in front of the altar where I pray at every day.  Sometimes I hold on to those horns just because I need it for that day.  But the September month was laid on the ground, and I was instructed to stand on the month of September and begin to pray for several things specifically.  I was instructed to pray for the church to have a strong backbone, for corruption in the church to be exposed, and for a great harvest.  And so I stand on the calendar, and I begin to pray for those things.  And as I'm praying, I hear a voice that says, you're not enough.  We need more people praying, so ask for more help.  So as I'm standing on the calendar, I'm calling out pastors, people, believers, whoever you are, we need to pray for the church to have a strong backbone, for corruption to be exposed, and for a great harvest.
